title: Doughnut Plant - Shop & Central Kitchen
description: Donut shop with multiple outlets in the city - this one is at 東京都武蔵野市吉祥寺東町2-18-16. Makes egg-free donuts from natural ingredients. Offers vegan varieties, including a baked soy milk doughnut and a baked soy milk caramel doughnut plus a couple seasonally changing ones. Flour and malt imported from the U.S. Uses brown sugar from organic sugar cane.
